oai_dc:dc.dc:title: George Washington Campbell
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: George Washington Campbell held the following positions: U.S. Congressman, 1803-1809; U.S. Senator, 1811-1814, 1815-1818; Secretary of Treasury for Madison, 1814; Minister to Russia, 1818-1821.
